Whiteboard Tab is  the ultimate chrome extension that transforms your new tab into a versatile digital canvas. With Whiteboard Tab, you can unleash your creativity and productivity by drawing, sketching, and jotting down ideas right on your browser's new tab page. Whiteboard tab will also provide you the weather and temperature.

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to install the Whiteboard Tab extension and set the new tab search to that provided by the service. The search will be powered by Yahoo.

This user-friendly extension provides a seamless and intuitive interface, allowing you to effortlessly express your thoughts and visualize concepts without any hassle. As soon as you open a new tab, the Whiteboard Tab canvas greets you with a blank space, ready to capture your imagination.
